summary: Check PrepareArtifact plugin
description: |
    Test coverage for all artifact provider types.
    Each provider is tested separately in its own subdirectory:
    - koji: Tests koji.build provider (fetch from Koji build ID)
    - file: Tests file provider (local RPM file)
    - repository-url: Tests repository-url provider (remote .repo file)
    - combined: Tests all providers working together in a single prepare step
